    - rid: 5422256147352781317
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: 'Hey, who are you?! '
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781318
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Relax, I heard you were robbed. I'm looking for that thief.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781319
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: He robbed my cornfield. Most of what was growing. Good thing I chased
          him away in time.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781320
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I saw him running towards the warehouse, but it was dark and I don't
          know where he went. You can ask the bartender about the warehouse. He has
          a key there.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781321
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: What do you want to know?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781322
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Tell me what happened
    - rid: 5422256147352781323
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: What did he look like?
    - rid: 5422256147352781324
      type: {class: OptionItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Okay, I will find him.
    - rid: 5422256147352781325
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Dark skin color, like a thief's...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781326
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: ...black bandana on the head...
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781327
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: ...and it smelled terrible
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781328
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: I found this bastard.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781329
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Great news!
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781330
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Did he have my corn?
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781331
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Unfortunately not.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781332
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422256147352781333
      type: {class: RandomItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Flow, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data: 
    - rid: 5422256147352781334
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: It's good that you came to town.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781335
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Come back next year, I bet you've never eaten corn like this.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
    - rid: 5422256147352781336
      type: {class: ConversationItem, ns: EasyTalk.Nodes.Common, asm: games.okitoki.EasyTalk}
      data:
        text: Get out! Go to bartender, he knows something.
        audioClip: {fileID: 0}
        audioClipFile: 
        audioAssetID: 0
